20060281.text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Haeryongsanmaek</> was recently discovered and most of the leylines have been closed.\n<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Younggyowon</>

20060282.text: (After checking closely, these people are also <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Pungbaekmun</>.

20060284.text: (I think this way is the right way... It's better to signal to people after \n safety is secured, rather than noticing too soon)

20060285.text: (<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Arang</> is right. Let's hurry to <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Search Post</> from now on)

20060286.text: (Did Arang really go first? It sounds like you're offended...\nLet's go after work!)
